## vue3一个全局提示弹窗

> 一种新的写法

toast.vue

```html
<template>
  <transition-group class="toast-wrap" tag="div">
    <div
      class="toast"
      v-for="toast in toastArr"
      :id="toast.id"
      :key="toast.id">
      {{ toast.content }}
    </div>
  </transition-group>
</template>

<script>
import { ref, unref } from 'vue'
export default {
  name: 'toast',
  setup (props, { expose }) {
    // 管理所有的id
    const toastArr = ref([])

    let id = 0

    // 生成id
    const uuid = () => `toast_${id++}`

    /**
     * 添加add的toast
     * @param toast{Object}
     * @doc toast参数是个对象，接受content与duration两个参数
     *
     */
    const add = (toast) => {
      const id = uuid()

      // // 生成v-for循环数组的项toast-item，除去不必要的响应式
      unref(toastArr).push({
        ...toast,
        id
      })

      // 默认清除时间
      const { duration = 3 } =  toast
      // 设置定时器
      const timer = setTimeout(() => {
        remove(id)
        clearTimeout(timer)
      }, duration)
    }

    // 根据 id 删除消息对象
    const remove = (id) => {
      toastArr.value = unref(toastArr).filter(item => item.id !== id)
    }

    expose({ add, remove })

    return {
      toastArr
    }
  }
}
</script>
<style scoped lang="scss">
    .toast{
        background: red;
    }
</style>
```

toast.js

```js
import { render, createVNode } from 'vue'
import toastComponent from './toast.vue'

let instance

function getInstance () {
  if (instance) return
  const divNode = document.createElement('div')
  instance = createVNode(toastComponent)

  // 渲染实例
  render(instance, divNode)

  // 插入子节点
  document.body.appendChild(divNode)
}

export default function tosat ({content = '', duration}) {
  getInstance()
  instance.component.exposed.add({
    content,
    duration
  })
}
```
